title: Dakine Shyla Shoulder Bag
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Shyla Shoulder Bag in our Vienna print.
Shyla Features:
- Interior padded laptop sleeve
- Fits most 17" laptops
- Vinyl trims
- Adjustable cross body shoulder strap
- Metal hardware
- Turn-lock closure
- Exterior zippered pocket
- Interior organizer pocket
- Nylon lining
